Date: Wed, 15 Jul 2026 12:49:07 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] [PATCH] Update the time crate (bsc#1257912, CVE-2026-25727)

Update the time crate to version 0.3.47 to deal
with bsc#1257912, CVE-2026-25727.

Of course, this does not work if the vendor.tar.zst. So, in order for
this patch to be effective, the package maintainers need to run the
following commands (in the package sources):

osc service manualrun
cd virtiofsd
patch -p1 < ../update-time-0.3.47.patch
mkdir .cargo
cargo vendor > .cargo/config.toml
tar -I zstd -cf vendor.tar.zst vendor/ .cargo/
mv vendor.tar.zst ..

Signed-off-by: Dario Faggioli <dfaggioli@suse.com>
